Sentencas: Thin films of PrBaCo2O5+delta (PBCO) were prepared on SrTiO3 substrates by spray pyrolysis.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity relaxation of polycrystalline PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: Electrical conductivity relaxation was performed to measure the surface exchange coefficient, k(chem),, from 650 to 850 K, in the pO(2) range 0.05-100% at a total pressure of 1 atm.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity relaxation of polycrystalline PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: The measured values fell in the range from 3.4 x 10(-9) cm/s to 8.6 x 10(-7) cm/s, with an activation energy of 1.30 eV.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity relaxation of polycrystalline PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: These values are significantly lower, and the activation energy higher, than previous reports.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity relaxation of polycrystalline PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: This discrepancy, and the discrepancies between prior reports in the literature, are attributed to surface composition.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity relaxation of polycrystalline PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: The film samples used in this study are shown to be enriched in (Pr + Ba) when compared with the bulk composition.
